      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FROG MARCH (2) was unfancied last time out but hit the ground running to lead all the way, scoring by 6 lengths (22.78) at this track in a Mix 3/4 over 400m. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from five starts. Expected to go well again. DUBROW (1) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd over 525m at The Meadows beaten 2 lengths (30.20) behind Doongalla Pedro in a Grade 5 on March 11. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can feature again. PRINCE LAROI (7) quickly away to win over the 400m at this track two runs back then settled forward again when finishing second at Ballarat last start. Expected to be in the finish again. RIDICULOUS (8) looks a chance coming off a six-and-a-half weeks layoff.",
